  "error": "CSV body must be a non-empty string. Set Content-Type: text/csv"
}

request.description:
**Request body:**
```json
{ "addresses": ["G...", "G..."] }
```
- Maximum 200 addresses per request. Exceeding this returns `400`.
- Non-string entries are silently filtered out.

**Expected 200 response:**
```json
{
  "results": [
    { "address": "GAAZI4...", "verified": true },
    { "address": "GBVVJJ...", "verified": false },
    { "address": "GDQOE2...", "verified": true }
  ]
}
```

**Request constraints:**
- `recipients` array: 1–1000 items
- `address`: exactly 56 characters
- `amountStroops`: whole-number string (no decimals)

**Expected 200 response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "routes": [
      {
        "type": "transfer",
        "recipient": "GAAZI4...",
        "amountStroops": "10000000"
      },
      {
        "type": "invoke_contract",
        "contractId": "CAAAAA...",
        "functionName": "deposit",
        "args": { "recipient": "CAAAAA...", "amountStroops": "50000000" },
        "vault": {
          "contractId": "CAAAAA...",
          "name": "StellarStream Vault",
          "depositFunction": "deposit",
          "minDepositStroops": null
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

response.body:
{
  "success": false,
  "error": "Must be a whole number string"
}

request.description:
Lists all active members of the organisation. Requires at least `DRAFTER` role.

**Expected 200 response:**
```json
{
  "orgAddress": "GAAZI4...",
  "members": [
    { "memberAddress": "GBVVJJ...", "role": "EXECUTOR", "addedBy": "GAAZI4...", "isActive": true },
    { "memberAddress": "GDQOE2...", "role": "DRAFTER",  "addedBy": "GAAZI4...", "isActive": true }
  ]
}
```

